<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对 她就是个纯粹的笨蛋 这也算是她的优点</font>

165
00:11:00,449 --> 00:11:04,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实我很明白 错的人是我</font>

166
00:11:06,449 --> 00:11:13,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我只是得到了她的心脏 就自认为继承了她的遗志</font>

167
00:11:14,369 --> 00:11:18,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但为什么夏凪你会想要继承谢丝塔的职责？</font>

168
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:25,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我从小身体就不好</font>

169
00:11:25,759 --> 00:11:30,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">本来以为自己永远无法离开那个活像鸟笼的病房</font>

170
00:11:31,739 --> 00:11:35,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">觉得自己将来肯定会一事无成吧</font>

171
00:11:36,809 --> 00:11:38,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这让我非常害怕</font>

172
00:11:40,549 --> 00:11:46,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是我得到了新的生命 让我能飞出那个鸟笼</font>

173
00:11:47,089 --> 00:11:47,749
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过…</font>

174
00:11:49,479 --> 00:11:52,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我不知道该如何飞翔</font>

175
00:11:52,829 --> 00:11:53,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如何飞翔？</font>

176
00:11:54,579 --> 00:12:03,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对 所以我才想依靠这个心脏 走上她的人生道路</font>

177
00:12:05,379 --> 00:12:11,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原来如此 夏凪只有依靠着谢丝塔才能活下去</font>

178
00:12:12,039 --> 00:12:14,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而我也是一样</font>

179
00:12:15,979 --> 00:12:16,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉</font>

180
00:12:18,049 --> 00:12:19,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我先回去休息了</font>

181
00:12:20,829 --> 00:12:21,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好…</font>

182
00:12:36,969 --> 00:12:40,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">重复一遍 通知船上的各位乘客</font>

183
00:12:41,279 --> 00:12:44,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 这个广播是怎么回事？是从哪儿传出来的！</font>

184
00:12:44,879 --> 00:12:48,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">无线电室没人啊！到底怎么回事</font>

185
00:12:49,459 --> 00:12:50,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">搞什么？</font>

186
00:12:50,949 --> 00:12:55,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我在大厅带走了一位女孩</font>

187
00:12:55,489 --> 00:12:57,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">女孩的名字叫…</font>

188
00:12:57,729 --> 00:12:59,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">「夏凪渚」</font>

189
00:13:00,529 --> 00:13:01,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">君冢！</font>

190
00:13:03,539 --> 00:13:04,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">斋川！</font>

191
00:13:04,769 --> 00:13:09,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我去了渚的房间 但到处都找不到她</font>

192
00:13:14,659 --> 00:13:19,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就是说 那位「谢丝塔」的遗产和这次事件有关？</font>

193
00:13:19,719 --> 00:13:22,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对 无法排除这个可能性</font>

194
00:13:25,709 --> 00:13:26,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">夏凪小姐呢？</font>

195
00:13:27,679 --> 00:13:28,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">斋川小姐</font>

196
00:13:29,519 --> 00:13:31,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">很遗憾 我们没能发现</font>

197
00:13:31,739 --> 00:13:32,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(福尔摩斯短篇集)</font>

198
00:13:32,099 --> 00:13:33,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是找到了这个东西
(福尔摩斯短篇集)</font>

199
00:13:33,459 --> 00:13:33,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(福尔摩斯短篇集)</font>

200
00:13:38,539 --> 00:13:40,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">君冢 你看这个</font>

201
00:13:41,789 --> 00:13:41,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(下午8点 带上大侦探的遗产 来主甲板)</font>

202
00:13:41,919 --> 00:13:46,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">「下午8点 带上大侦探的遗产来主甲板」
(下午8点 带上大侦探的遗产 来主甲板)</font>

203
00:13:46,719 --> 00:13:46,829
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">「下午8点 带上大侦探的遗产来主甲板」</font>

204
00:13:48,949 --> 00:13:50,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是SPES吗？</font>

205
00:13:51,069 --> 00:13:56,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果是冲着大侦探的遗产来的 那间接证据是够了</font>

206
00:13:57,119 --> 00:14:00,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但不巧的是 我也不知道那是什么</font>

207
00:14:01,929 --> 00:14:03,139
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">既然如此…</font>

208
00:14:07,189 --> 00:14:11,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那只能不去管谢丝塔的遗产 而是直接找夏凪</font>

209
00:14:32,319 --> 00:14:34,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这里也不行吗</font>

210
00:14:34,789 --> 00:14:38,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我用上了左眼 应该不会看漏</font>

211
00:14:39,619 --> 00:14:41,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也是…</font>

212
00:14:46,209 --> 00:14:47,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">有人握着你的手</font>

213
00:14:48,999 --> 00:14:52,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">放松肩膀 让呼吸变得有节奏</font>

214
00:14:53,819 --> 00:14:57,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">闭上眼睛深深吸气 再吐出来</font>

215
00:14:58,299 --> 00:14:59,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">血液在体内流动</font>

216
00:15:00,479 --> 00:15:04,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">张开眼睛 原本浑浊的视野变得无比清晰</font>

217
00:15:05,599 --> 00:15:07,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么意思？</font>

218
00:15:07,619 --> 00:15:13,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在演唱会开场前 让我紧张得快炸开的心平静下来的咒语</font>

219
00:15:17,689 --> 00:15:21,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉 让你费心了 真是不像话</font>

220
00:15:21,969 --> 00:15:24,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不像话？你说你自己吗？</font>

221
00:15:25,019 --> 00:15:27,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是啊 就这么乱了阵脚 实在难堪</font>

222
00:15:29,239 --> 00:15:30,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这话说得真有意思</font>

223
00:15:31,559 --> 00:15:36,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我本来就没对你抱有多大期望哦</font>

224
00:15:36,529 --> 00:15:40,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我现在算是被疯狂挖苦了吗？</font>

225
00:15:41,009 --> 00:15:43,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">讨厌 不是啦</font>

226
00:15:46,529 --> 00:15:48,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我当初也一样</font>

227
00:15:49,319 --> 00:15:49,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一样？</font>

228
00:15:50,779 --> 00:15:55,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我当初也和君冢一样 是没法独自活下去的人</font>

229
00:15:57,429 --> 00:16:04,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">父母去世 失去了人生的方向 只剩那过去的约定束缚着我</font>

230
00:16:04,969 --> 00:16:09,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">结果就是差点做出了无可挽回的错事</font>

231
00:16:10,299 --> 00:16:11,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">斋川…</font>

232
00:16:12,679 --> 00:16:19,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但救了当初那个我的 偏偏就是应该和我一样的君冢</font>

233
00:16:19,739 --> 00:16:21,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">或者说是渚</font>

234
00:16:22,189 --> 00:16:26,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你们两个拯救了我 让我继续向前迈进</font>

235
00:16:27,349 --> 00:16:31,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以我才能毫不犹豫地握住你们的手</font>

236
00:16:32,239 --> 00:16:37,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以 虽然很对不起 但我不会对君冢产生超出必要的期待</font>

237
00:16:38,289 --> 00:16:43,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而君冢你也不用对我有超出必要的顾虑</font>

238
00:16:43,909 --> 00:16:47,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为我们就是这样的同伴啊</font>

239
00:16:48,479 --> 00:16:51,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 这样就好…这样才好</font>

240
00:16:52,349 --> 00:16:58,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果君冢是大侦探的助手 那我就当助手的助手也好</font>

241
00:16:58,819 --> 00:17:01,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大侦探的助手的助手？</font>

242
00:17:01,419 --> 00:17:05,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 对啊 感觉就跟套娃一样了</font>

243
00:17:06,339 --> 00:17:09,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然我不知道自己能否成为你的左右手</font>

244
00:17:09,509 --> 00:17:11,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但当个左眼应该没问题</font>

245
00:17:12,699 --> 00:17:14,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 那可真是让人放心</font>

246
00:17:20,219 --> 00:17:23,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">结果一路走到这里 什么都没能找到</font>

247
00:17:23,979 --> 00:17:25,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是 君冢</font>

248
00:17:25,659 --> 00:17:29,749
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 至少得到了「什么都没能找到」的成果</font>

249
00:17:31,249 --> 00:17:34,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也就是说 哪怕是斋川的左眼 也没法找到敌人</font>

250
00:17:35,349 --> 00:17:36,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">有什么头绪吗？</font>

251
00:17:37,409 --> 00:17:41,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 接下来不需要推理 也不需要策略</font>

252
00:17:42,969 --> 00:17:45,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而是全面开战啊 混蛋</font>

253
00:17:56,329 --> 00:17:58,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我已经受够兜圈子了</font>

254
00:18:00,229 --> 00:18:04,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">赶快给我出来 变色龙 把夏凪渚还给我！</font>

255
00:18:06,209 --> 00:18:08,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没想到你能察觉到啊</font>

256
00:18:15,589 --> 00:18:16,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">夏凪！</font>

257
00:18:16,479 --> 00:18:17,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">等等</font>

258
00:18:20,179 --> 00:18:22,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">请你待在那里别动</font>

259
00:18:25,539 --> 00:18:27,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你的目的是什么？</font>

260
00:18:27,739 --> 00:18:31,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">目的？我早就告诉过你了</font>

261
00:18:31,569 --> 00:18:37,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我倒是很想给你遗产 但不好意思 我也不知道那是什么</font>

262
00:18:38,189 --> 00:18:40,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">能不能乖乖交出夏凪呢</font>

263
00:18:41,269 --> 00:18:43,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这可就头疼啦</font>

264
00:18:45,109 --> 00:18:48,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这样可根本算不上交易了</font>

265
00:18:50,039 --> 00:18:51,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给我住手 变色龙！</font>

266
00:18:59,159 --> 00:19:00,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">君…冢？</font>

267
00:19:01,689 --> 00:19:02,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">夏凪！</font>

268
00:19:07,579 --> 00:19:11,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我好像失手了 抱歉</font>

269
00:19:16,449 --> 00:19:17,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好吧</font>

270
00:19:18,569 --> 00:19:20,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那么 是要这个少女的生命</font>

271
00:19:20,969 --> 00:19:25,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">-还是现在正在拼命避难的那些乘客的生命 -大家冷静点！这边走！</font>

272
00:19:27,619 --> 00:19:30,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">请你做出选择吧</font>

273
00:19:30,859 --> 00:19:33,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你做这种事又有什么意义？</font>

274
00:19:33,879 --> 00:19:36,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只是顺手而已</font>

275
00:19:36,759 --> 00:19:37,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">顺手？</font>

276
00:19:38,259 --> 00:19:42,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对 既然找不到大侦探的遗产</font>

277
00:19:42,419 --> 00:19:44,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那只要把整艘船都弄沉就行</font>

278
00:19:46,059 --> 00:19:51,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那夏凪呢？要她的命对你们有什么好处！</font>

279
00:19:51,829 --> 00:19:54,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原因很简单</font>

280
00:19:54,639 --> 00:19:58,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个少女的体内有大侦探的血啊</font>

281
00:20:00,269 --> 00:20:02,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好了 做出选择吧</font>

282
00:20:03,169 --> 00:20:06,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是要这个少女的命 还是乘客的命</font>

283
00:20:11,209 --> 00:20:12,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">君冢…</font>

284
00:20:17,049 --> 00:20:18,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">朝我开枪</font>

285
00:20:19,769 --> 00:20:21,829
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说什么啊 夏凪</font>

286
00:20:22,449 --> 00:20:23,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">朝我开枪</font>

287
00:20:24,899 --> 00:20:28,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">拯救乘客的生命 不就是最正确的答案吗</font>

288
00:20:29,079 --> 00:20:32,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这种理性逻辑的思维 可真不是你的风格啊</font>

289
00:20:33,299 --> 00:20:35,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗 也许吧</font>

290
00:20:37,119 --> 00:20:41,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但现在这个情况 需要的不是我的激情</font>

291
00:20:42,689 --> 00:20:44,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而是大侦探的理性</font>

292
00:20:45,179 --> 00:20:46,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你不就是大侦探吗</font>

293
00:20:47,509 --> 00:20:50,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不对 我什么都不是</font>

294
00:20:52,859 --> 00:20:53,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">君冢</font>

295
00:20:54,849 --> 00:21:01,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你对我说 「不用想着去代替什么人」 让我非常高兴</font>

296
00:21:03,939 --> 00:21:04,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢谢</font>

297
00:21:14,249 --> 00:21:16,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我才不需要这种正确</font>

298
00:21:18,379 --> 00:21:20,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说你什么都不是？</font>

299
00:21:21,639 --> 00:21:25,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">既然什么都不是 那不就意味着将来有着无限可能吗</font>

300
00:21:27,129 --> 00:21:31,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不知道怎么飞翔 那就向别人学习怎么扑腾翅膀</font>

301
00:21:33,099 --> 00:21:37,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不知道人生道路该怎么走 那就和别人并肩前行</font>

302
00:21:41,829 --> 00:21:44,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">应该得出答案了吧？</font>

303
00:21:44,869 --> 00:21:48,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对 答案早就注定了</font>

304
00:21:54,489 --> 00:21:59,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我绝对不会让夏凪渚先我而死</font>

305
00:22:00,419 --> 00:22:03,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉 这是我们许下的约定</font>

306
00:22:06,509 --> 00:22:11,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">每次醒来 你都在我身边</font>

307
00:22:11,879 --> 00:22:17,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给我一个全新的早晨</font>

308
00:22:17,029 --> 00:22:22,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那心跳是如此温柔</font>

309
00:22:22,409 --> 00:22:27,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又悲伤得催人泪下</font>

310
00:22:27,729 --> 00:22:33,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在大声叫喊著 想要见到某人</font>

311
00:22:33,079 --> 00:22:38,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又不知道名字和长相</font>

312
00:22:38,409 --> 00:22:43,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我真的听到了那声音</font>

313
00:22:43,729 --> 00:22:48,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只能漫无目的地去探寻</font>

314
00:22:48,689 --> 00:22:53,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然可能只会徒增烦恼</font>

315
00:22:54,029 --> 00:23:02,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但这不是为了别人而是为了自己</font>

316
00:23:03,869 --> 00:23:09,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">胸膛中的声音 那声呐喊 指引着我前进</font>

317
00:23:09,169 --> 00:23:14,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将零落的心意捡起 送到它想去的地方吧</font>

318
00:23:14,489 --> 00:23:19,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为是你告诉我生命的意义</font>

319
00:23:19,739 --> 00:23:27,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让我觉得 这个世界也许还没那么坏</font>

320
00:23:35,929 --> 00:23:40,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(第11集 希望中的光芒)</font>

